{"tid":1758501,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建議國際文宣應該分番開”真中國人”同”支那人”","createTime":"2019-11-27T05:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T09:21:06.000Z","uid":128229,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb107b8244cf848a8002f75ffc8d76b71f5633a","tid":1758501,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"而家香港攪左咁多個月<br />\n開始星星之火燎原緊上面<br />\n而家好多大陸人唔多唔少都覺醒緊<br />\n情況就似十年前香港<br />\n所以我地應該統一番一班支持民主，自由，以普世價值為重既真中國人<br />\n而唔係一碌鳩打沉成船人<br />\n多個朋友好過多個敵人<br />\n至於果班中共 共青團 小粉紅 無腦藍絲 一律歸屬為支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df010de2f38bcbf08e9db461ebc3fe226f05014a","tid":1758501,"uid":45369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"事實係咁"},{"pid":"4e539588d739a3c0d1aa0d58cf06e7d1df4f332a","tid":1758501,"uid":201512,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"品蔥的中國手足都係叫佢地身邊班粉紅叫支那人。<br />\n所以唔需要特別避忌，直接叫愛共的五毛叫支那，擁護民主的中國人會明白唔係話佢地"},{"pid":"be1cc079d15e4bdaab74a9517bed5b069c06fe39","tid":1758501,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vq2VS6P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVq2VS6P.jpg&h=df2259db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKP5vTv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKP5vTv.jpg&h=24d6f0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"baf55d16d65d9a086117b14cb32cc7c4d7325082","tid":1758501,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:10:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f458f1ec0e6444d8a1294ba5280b43075b990db5","tid":1758501,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e539588d739a3c0d1aa0d58cf06e7d1df4f332a","tid":1758501,"uid":201512,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"品蔥的中國手足都係叫佢地身邊班粉紅叫支那人。<br />\n所以唔需要特別避忌，直接叫愛共的五毛叫支那，擁護民主的中國人會明白唔係話佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"但好多海外華人，真中國人一聽支那就以為話埋佢地<br />\n所以要同佢地分番開話比佢地知<br />\n我相信呢個就係支共最驚既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d77e291a85325b4614f9f03d87a79b8392a3bf5","tid":1758501,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"我都係咁樣諗<br />\n劣質既叫支那人<br />\nOkge叫中國人<br />\n咪撚逼我叫自己中國人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e33748d3ce9478fa01014eee9ba9cf85c85db8","tid":1758501,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d77e291a85325b4614f9f03d87a79b8392a3bf5","tid":1758501,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"我都係咁樣諗<br />\n劣質既叫支那人<br />\nOkge叫中國人<br />\n咪撚逼我叫自己中國人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:21:06.000Z","msg":"仲之就要火燒支共後欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}